20:33.366 --> 20:36.937
This is fucking stupid, man.

20:36.970 --> 20:39.973
This is like really fucking
stupid, you're 20 years old.

20:40.007 --> 20:42.475
I'm 22!

20:42.509 --> 20:44.577
Okay, you're 22 years old,

20:44.611 --> 20:46.513
