22:09.196 --> 22:11.531
- Nice to meet you.
- Nice to meet you, too.

22:11.564 --> 22:14.667
Eh, congratulations on
the Sandquist-Wells merger.

22:14.701 --> 22:16.403
Thank you.

22:16.436 --> 22:18.938
