22:23.276 --> 22:25.712
So, uh, glasses, rocks?

22:25.745 --> 22:26.846
Anybody?
Who's up?

22:26.879 --> 22:29.949
- Not now.
- Maybe later.

22:29.983 --> 22:31.551
- I'll have a...
- Neat, right?

22:31.584 --> 22:32.719
Yeah.

22:32.752 --> 22:33.853
Hey, Nathan, I heard you're
in law school,

22:33.886 --> 22:35.788
