24:36.843 --> 24:39.246
He's not gonna have a choice,
he's gonna have to step up.

24:39.279 --> 24:40.880
You know some
of the greatest fortunes

24:40.913 --> 24:41.814
In the history
of the United States

24:41.848 --> 24:43.550
