27:17.036 --> 27:19.839
The way that you move.

27:19.872 --> 27:22.909
You probably studied dance
as a child.

27:22.942 --> 27:25.912
Which means that your parents
probably had money.

27:25.945 --> 27:27.547
Either that or they
sacrificed a lot

27:27.580 --> 27:29.916
To give you the things
that you needed.

27:31.117 --> 27:34.354
They were uh, hard workers.

27:34.387 --> 27:37.924
Good ethics,
emphasis on discipline.

27:37.957 --> 27:39.926
They didn't approve
of the way that you dressed

27:39.959 --> 27:41.561
Or the little tattoo
that you have on the inside

27:41.594 --> 27:43.530
