didn't care because

27:43.563 --> 27:45.097
You were rebellious.

27:45.131 --> 27:47.266
You know, if Henry
met your parents,

27:47.300 --> 27:49.769
He would really like them.

27:49.802 --> 27:52.271
He would admire
their work ethic,

27:52.305 --> 27:56.743
But that's very unlikely
to happen any time soon.

27:56.776 --> 27:59.011
Henry barely
acknowledges you.

27:59.045 --> 28:00.012
